                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-145-off826 t18290219-145-cd827"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290219-145-victim1356" type="victimName">
                           Elisha 
